00:09:28.463 --> 00:09:34.413
comes from his belief that there should only be one religion in Saudi Arabia, Islam.

00:09:35.643 --> 00:09:39.913
Bin Laden would later teach his followers that the Prophet Mohammed, on his

00:09:39.913 --> 00:09:44.403
deathbed, said that there should only ever be one religion in Saudi Arabia.

00:09:45.373 --> 00:09:50.173
By allowing Western troops into Saudi Arabia, no matter whether the intentions

00:09:50.173 --> 00:09:55.613
were to fight Sadam Hussein, and defend Saudi Arabia, this was going directly

00:09:55.633 --> 00:10:00.123
against the wishes of the prophet, at least in Osama bin Laden’s interpretation.

00:10:01.603 --> 00:10:08.733
So, Osama bin Laden set out on his lifelong mission to get US troops out of the Middle East.

00:10:09.873 --> 00:10:16.363
On this mission, it’s hard to argue that he succeeded, as there is no individual in history

00:10:16.663 --> 00:10:21.443
who has done more to increase the Western presence in the Middle East than Osama bin Laden.

00:10:22.583 --> 00:10:24.626
